last message relating to it is received and filed.

<h2>Find a bug report by reference number</h2>

<form method="get" action="http://cgi.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugs-fetch.pl">
<input type="hidden" name="type" value="ref">
<input type="text" size="10" name="ref" value="">
<input type="hidden" name="base" value="http://www.debian.org">
<input type="submit" value="Fetch">
</form>

<h2>Find a bug report by package</h2>

<form method="get" action="http://cgi.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugs-fetch.pl">
